WEBVTT

00:00.396 --> 00:03.015
Shaping the future with physical AI.

00:03.562 --> 00:06.299
Neural D introduces next-generation

00:06.324 --> 00:08.428
autonomous inspection technology.

00:09.887 --> 00:13.150
ADS is an AI-powered inspection solution

00:13.405 --> 00:15.311
that identifies and diagnoses

00:15.335 --> 00:18.910
vast numbers of power grid assets in real time.

00:19.854 --> 00:21.810
Even while moving at high speed,

00:22.376 --> 00:26.822
detecting cracks and pinpointing components that require attention.

00:27.389 --> 00:29.411
Powered by physical AI,

00:29.923 --> 00:31.568
Neural D's ADS

00:31.594 --> 00:35.251
delivers fast and highly accurate autonomous diagnostics

00:35.498 --> 00:37.348
across the entire network.

00:44.214 --> 00:45.509
Mounted on vehicles,

01:12.775 --> 01:14.879
At the core of ADS are

01:36.914 --> 01:41.219
ADS dramatically reduces asset maintenance time and cost.

01:42.203 --> 01:45.233
Enabling efficient management of power grid assets

01:45.295 --> 01:47.395
spread across vast regions.

01:48.600 --> 01:50.486
Neural D's breakthrough technology,

01:50.613 --> 01:52.928
proven through years of collaboration with KEPCO,

01:53.029 --> 01:54.995
has been recognized with top honors,

02:03.061 --> 02:06.538
Our diagnostic technologies are protected by patents

02:06.620 --> 02:08.019
not only in Korea,

02:08.204 --> 02:13.154
but also in the United States, Saudi Arabia, Japan, and Vietnam.

02:13.976 --> 02:17.804
Neural D is expanding beyond visual diagnostics,

02:17.829 --> 02:19.869
advancing thermal imaging,

02:19.894 --> 02:22.520
ultrasonic inspection, and more.

02:33.736 --> 02:38.115
We will deliver unparalleled
AI driven inspection technology

02:38.140 --> 02:41.170
across an even wider range of industries.
